    ComponentImplementedI, DataOfferedI.PullI, DataOfferedI.PushI, OfferedI, RequiredI, DataInboundPortI, InboundPortI, PortI, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class RNGDataInboundPort
extends AbstractDataInboundPort
implements DataOfferedI.PullI, DataOfferedI.PushI
    The class RNGDataInboundPort implements the inbound port of a component of type RNGProducerI offering a random number generation service through the data offered interface RNGDataOfferedI.

    Description

    The get method (from the pull interface of the data offered component interface) calls the method produce from its RNGProducerI owner component to get a new random number..

    Invariant

     invariant      this.owner instanceof RNGProducerI
